@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Swagger docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login and save token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Get all announcements
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements

### Create announcement with image
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Продам велосипед
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Trek у відмінному стані
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

8500
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

sale
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contactInfo"

veloman@gmail.com
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="sample-image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-image.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### Create announcement without image
POST {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Оголошення без фото
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Тестове оголошення без картинки
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

100
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

sale
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="contactInfo"

test@gmail.com
--WebAppBoundary--

### Update announcement with image
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Оновлена назва
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="sample-image.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-image.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### CORS allowed origin test
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Origin: http://localhost:5173

### CORS denied origin test - should return 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/announcements
Origin: http://evil.com

